cs.LG, cs.CV, cs.CR, cs.AI, cs.NE 

The paper discusses the vulnerability of deep neural networks to adversarial examples, which is a common topic in the sub-fields of machine learning (cs.LG), computer vision (cs.CV), and cybersecurity (cs.CR). The proposed method involves exploiting the frequency domain, which is a technique commonly used in signal processing and image analysis, indicating a possible fit for the sub-field of artificial intelligence (cs.AI) as well. Additionally, the use of neural networks in the proposed method suggests a possible fit for the sub-field of neural networks (cs.NE).
